The '''Alsakan Circo-Menagerie''' was a popular traveling show during the height of the [[Galactic Republic/Legends|Old Republic]]. It combined the entertainment of the [[Circus/Legends|circus]] with the thrill of [[Alien/Legends|alien]] groups such as the [[Gados|Gado]] [[Leaping Tee]]s.<ref name="CCW">''[[Coruscant and the Core Worlds]]''</ref>

